                        <h1>December 3, 2008</h1>                                  
                        Do you jump for joy when your cholesterol drops five points? Do you enjoy seeing the occasional celebrity ogle at the latest consumer technology as they meander the aisles of CES? Do you make business decisions more comfortably when you have the hard data to back them up? Then this edition of CES Up to the Minute is just for you. Enjoy, and get ready for the <A href="http://www.CESweb.org">2009 International CES</A>, January 8-11, in Las Vegas, Nevada. It’s the one place to put your finger on the pulse of consumer technology and see the heart of innovation.

