<a name="2638"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">TechZone Spotlight: Digital Health</div>
<br />
<STRONG><IMG height=118 src="/print/images/content/MH_blu-darkblu2.jpg" width=226 align=right border=0>Location: Sands<BR>Sponsored by Meridian Health<BR></STRONG><BR><A href="/print/exhibits/displays/techZones.asp#2451">The Digital Health TechZone</A> features emerging technologies and innovative companies using home and person-based options for disrupting the traditional delivery of health and wellness services. See the transformation and creation of new consumer-centric connections between patients and healthcare providers. And while you’re there, visit the mobile diagnostic facility from Athletes for Life Foundation. More. <BR><BR>The Athletes for Life (AFL) Foundation is a partnership of world class athletes, medical professionals and key individuals working together to “Save Lives One Heart at a Time” by spreading information and education about Heart Disease and how it impacts everyone in America. Come visit their mobile diagnostic facility with revolutionary cardiovascular monitoring and testing technology in the LVCC, CES Central Plaza and within the Digital Health TechZone at the Sands.
